      "recording_attendee_id": "08fa437d-8c9a-4b91-995a-9b90955b4815",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "Yeah, so he works in Virginia um overseas that mark it looks like that's where you guys are located. Um But yeah, I just wanted to see in terms in terms of marketing we are, you know facebook and then obviously our our other platforms as well and work with senior services um along with other different types of apartment homes."
