      "recording_attendee_id": "4e15d331-9dc3-4923-82ff-64ea54b3b691",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "So, uh, our corporate offices are in Roanoke in Charleston, South Carolina, but we have properties in seven states. So I was just trying to identify what you were specifically interested in supporting."
