      "start_time": 178.87,
      "recording_attendee_id": "08fa437d-8c9a-4b91-995a-9b90955b4815",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "Yeah, honestly, I mean depending on kind of your needs and and that that kind of goes within the meeting too with then he could he could see that and and talk you through it, but we work nation, we're a nationwide company. Um so if there's certain properties that need help with with getting people in or um you know others that maybe are fully occupied. We we custom tailor um any packages and lists that go out to where needs maybe."
