      "text": "Okay. Okay. Yeah and and facebook is one of just the platforms that we use. Obviously we have other, like we have our website, we have other platforms that we use. So that's why we typically look to talk with someone in marketing, um, that handles that. But if that's where you think it might be best suited, I can definitely, you know, talk with her."
